      <title>土耳其调查财务主管辞职的虚假社交媒体帖子</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/turkey-probes-false-social-media-posts-that-finance-chief-quit</link>
      <description><![CDATA[土耳其资本市场委员会（SPK）周六宣布，土耳其正在调查社交媒体上错误宣称财政部长穆罕默德·西姆塞克已辞职的帖子，该帖子导致伊斯坦布尔证券交易所股价大幅下跌。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/turkey-probes-false-social-media-posts-that-finance-chief-quit</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 09:27:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国不会禁止债券交易但认为购买狂潮存在风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/china-won-t-ban-bond-trading-but-sees-risk-in-buying-frenzy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国人民银行没有寻求、也不会寻求禁止合法的投资或交易其国债，但其认为大举购买这些证券存在风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/china-won-t-ban-bond-trading-but-sees-risk-in-buying-frenzy</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 08:22:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧洲央行管委霍尔茨曼称9月降息并非“必然结果”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-holzmann-says-september-cut-isn-t-foregone-conclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行管理委员会委员罗伯特·霍尔茨曼警告称，尽管他的几位同事暗示将降息，但下个月不一定会降低利率。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/ecb-s-holzmann-says-september-cut-isn-t-foregone-conclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 07:54:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>争夺关键矿物刺激非洲铁路复兴</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/scramble-for-critical-minerals-spurs-an-african-rail-revival</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南部非洲的铁路突然受到全球关注，吸引了数十亿美元的投资，而其核心是争夺能源转型所需的铜供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/scramble-for-critical-minerals-spurs-an-african-rail-revival</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新加坡大亨被判有罪的豪宅以 300 万美元折扣出售</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/singapore-convicted-tycoon-s-mansion-sold-at-3-million-discount</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一名被判有罪的石油大亨的豪宅以比最初要价低近 400 万新元（310 万美元）的价格售出，这表明尽管销售有所回升，但新加坡的高端房地产市场的估值仍面临压力。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/singapore-convicted-tycoon-s-mansion-sold-at-3-million-discount</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 04:12:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>为什么 AMLO 的司法改革让投资者感到恐慌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/why-amlo-s-judicial-reform-is-spooking-investors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[即将离任的总统安德烈斯·曼努埃尔·洛佩斯·奥夫拉多尔再次颠覆了墨西哥的政治格局，推动通过一项将深刻改变该国司法系统的有争议的改革。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-24/why-amlo-s-judicial-reform-is-spooking-investors</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 24 Aug 2024 04:00:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
